The '''C-9969 landing craft''' was a modified version of the [[C-9979 landing craft/Legends|C-9979 landing craft]].

==Characteristics==
The C-9969 had a larger landing pedestal than the C-9979, allowing it to carry 12 [[Multi-Troop Transport/Legends|MTTs]], rather than eleven. It also had widened and elongated wings to fit 120 [[Armored Assault Tank/Legends|AATs]], rather than 114, and 30 [[Platoon Attack Craft/Legends|Trade Federation troop carriers]], rather than 28. It was manufactured by [[Haor Chall Engineering/Legends|Haor Chall Engineering]].

